title: Winter turns to spring
body:
Pairing: Jungkook x Reader

Warning: Angst

You thought dating an idol would be easy but really it’s not. You are in a relationship with one of the members of the most popular boy groups in the world, Jeon Jungkook. You never got to see him due to him always having a tight schedule. You missed his warm embrace that always brought happiness on your face. Many seasons past, winter has turned to spring. But when he isn’t around you everything turns into a mess. You have no one except him and the others to help you in the situation you are in.  Everywhere you go there would be fans that despise you with just one look at you, it hurts you that you have taken someone away from them that they cared and loved so much. You wished you could change everything. How will this end? 

Chapter 1
